       <div id="main-body">
        <h1>
         Welcome
        </h1>
        <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
         <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded">
           <p>
            Cornell Recreational Services offers a wide variety of fitness, wellness, sports and open recreation activities for Cornell students, staff, faculty, retirees and their spouses/partners. Through our broad-based programs, we try to promote a healthy and holistic lifestyle throughout the campus community.
           </p>
           <p>
            Recreational Services encompasses the
            <a href="/fitness">
             Cornell Fitness Centers
            </a>
            ,
            <a href="/bowling">
             Helen Newman Bowling Center
            </a>
            ,
            <a href="/hours-facilities/facilities">
             Helen Newman Hall Recreation Center
            </a>
            ,
            <a href="/intramurals">
             Intramural Sports
            </a>
            ,
            <a href="/noyes">
             Noyes Community Recreation Center
            </a>
            , and the
            <a href="/wellness">
             Cornell University Wellness Program
            </a>
            . Visit our
            <a href="/hours-facilities">
             Hours &amp; Facilities
            </a>
            page for more specific information on what we offer inside each facility and when we're open.
           </p>
           <p>
            Be sure to check out all of the other possibilities available to get out, get moving and have fun!
           </p>
           <ul>
            <li>
             Hike on the
             <a href="http://www.cornellbotanicgardens.org/trails">
              Cornell Botanic Gardens Nature Trails
             </a>
            </li>
            <li>
             Join a
             <a href="http://orgsync.rso.cornell.edu/SportClubs" target="_blank">
              sports club
             </a>
             —from archery to underwater hockey—there's something for everyone
            </li>
            <li>
             Skate at
             <a href="http://bigred2.athletics.cornell.edu/lynah/publicskate.html" target="_blank">
              Lynah Rink
             </a>
             during public skating hours
            </li>
            <li>
             Go backpacking or kayaking with
             <a href="http://coe.cornell.edu" target="_blank">
              Cornell Outdoor Education
             </a>
            </li>
            <li>
             Choose from over 100
             <a href="http://pe.cornell.edu/" target="_blank">
              Physical Education classes
             </a>
             open to students, staff and faculty each semester
            </li>
           </ul>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div id="col3">
        <div class="field field-name-field-column-3 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
         <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even">
           <h2 class="section">
            Recreation Special Events
           </h2>
           <h3>
            <a href="/home/rec-services-special-events">
             All Big Red Rec Special Events
            </a>
           </h3>
           <h3>
            <a href="mailto:bigredrec-info-l-request@cornell.edu?subject=Join">
             Join our list-serv
            </a>
            <br/>
            <br/>
           </h3>
           <h2 class="section">
            Follow Us
           </h2>
           <p>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/CornellFitnessCenters">
             <img alt="" src="/sites/recreation.athletics.cornell.edu/files/photos/facebook.gif" style="width: 32px; height: 32px;"/>
            </a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/cubigredrec">
             <img alt="" src="/sites/recreation.athletics.cornell.edu/files/photos/twitter.gif" style="width: 32px; height: 32px;"/>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bigredrec/">
             <img alt="" src="/sites/recreation.athletics.cornell.edu/files/photos/instagram-icon.png" style="width: 32px; height: 32px;"/>
            </a>
            <br/>
            <br/>
           </p>
           <h2 class="section">
            Free Recreation at Cornell
           </h2>
           <p>
            Your Cornell ID card is your ticket to free recreation on campus!
           </p>
           <ul>
            <li>
             Outdoor basketball on North or West Campus &amp; indoor at Helen Newman and Noyes
            </li>
            <li>
             Open lap swimming at Helen Newman or Teagle*
            </li>
            <li>
             Aqua ZUMBA
             <sup>
              ®
             </sup>
             at Teagle*
            </li>
            <li>
             Sand volleyball between Clara Dickson and Balch Hall
            </li>
            <li>
             Shoot pool or play table tennis at Noyes
            </li>
            <li>
             Tennis at Risley, Appel and Jessup courts
            </li>
            <li>
             Volleyball &amp; badminton at Helen Newman or Noyes
            </li>
            <li>
             Take a free PE class*
            </li>
            <li>
             Hike the Botanic Gardens trails
            </li>
           </ul>
           <p>
            *note: this offering free to students only; all others need membership.
           </p>
           <p>
            General
            <a href="/hours-facilities/equipment">
             equipment is available
            </a>
            to check out.
           </p>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
