<div class="content">
 <p>
  Working for Cornell Recreational Services–one of the largest employers of students on campus–is just plain fun.  Work for the Cornell Fitness Centers as a Fitness Monitor, a Group Fitness Instructor, Personal Trainer; or be an Intramural official or a Lifeguard.
  <a href="/employment">
   Learn more
  </a>
  .
